<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-14905] If SizeEstimatesRecorder misses a &apos;onDropTable&apos; notification, the size_estimates table will never be cleared for that table.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14905</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;if a node is down when a keyspace/table is dropped, it will receive the schema notification before the size estimates listener is registered, so the entries for the dropped keyspace/table will never be cleaned from the table.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
